"Biology"

"The book is divided into 6 parts. Part one concernes cell structure and function. Part two concernes the genetic basis of life. Part three explains the logical sequence of these topics: genetics, evolution, and diversity. Part four devotes to flowering plant anatomy and physiology, plant reproduction.Part five includes the very latest information on immunity, nutrition, the endocrine system, and development. Part six includes ecology and behavior"
" Sinh học đại cương"
